{"tid":550024,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴可唔可以做晒支停插？","createTime":"2018-02-04T10:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T12:21:45.000Z","uid":143206,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcd99d9a5f0ad07aff58c044eb7871d6b4252ee","tid":550024,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"支: 羊<br />\n停: ozil<br />\n插: 黑b 2wb<br />\n組織及拉邊: mk<br />\n後上: ramsey<br />\n派波及遠射: xka<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴成日對弱旅失分，如果可以轉踢主攻，就有更大機會解決弱隊<br />\n<br />\na山太多中場扭波，拖慢節奏，形成主攻陷阱，依家mk就唔會咁<br />\n<br />\nozil 體力不足，打防反尾段會無力，轉踢主攻比較適合佢<br />\n<br />\n對強隊要踢番防反，但起碼對弱隊主攻取3分，有利爭前4"},{"pid":"5c002a845d4f3f8e12e83214c46fb7bac0085764","tid":550024,"uid":12034,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"一直以黎阿仙奴就是主攻的代名詞"},{"pid":"c6b9dd8d568a2edee978ee06a225476f918da20e","tid":550024,"uid":8883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"主攻咪一樣輸反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得救架啦"},{"pid":"94fcee7289d5e3c066bd7fb9f2fb807f604fc56b","tid":550024,"uid":1167,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知你講乜 山神咁勁你有冇睇"},{"pid":"886b0c6ae7d3a5a685a7a187eb8039ef8a621487","tid":550024,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"Laca?"},{"pid":"cc92a0336ecc89cdd4f615cc71db78f25c058638","tid":550024,"uid":25900,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"炒人一場就打J打到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb202b8c52127f69f29558c7084981175c6ff25d","tid":550024,"uid":143206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94fcee7289d5e3c066bd7fb9f2fb807f604fc56b","tid":550024,"uid":1167,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知你講乜 山神咁勁你有冇睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:26:39.000Z","msg":"我有睇曼，山神較適合踢反擊，唔適合主攻，因為中場狂上腳，有時係幾勁，但變相拖慢左之餘，dispossess畀人打反擊都好煩，即係有利有弊，如果佢減少中場上腳就最好<br />\n<br />\n上年尼馬在巴塞亦係中場狂扭，結果巴塞上年成續麻麻，今年無尼馬反而重好"},{"pid":"b9808ecf81ffbb24bfd92b349be4b80c64416bc0","tid":550024,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886b0c6ae7d3a5a685a7a187eb8039ef8a621487","tid":550024,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"Laca?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"laca 有射術及速度，但整體意識一般，活動範圍亦唔夠大，做後備殺手比較好，負責在下半場改變戰局"},{"pid":"da40d9ed3f78dd56ff1b0dbfe7c1b002c649ba66","tid":550024,"uid":35538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"假對攻OK？"},{"pid":"a3c3f611ccd2c97ec583ddc03abf858560441ff9","tid":550024,"uid":143206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c6b9dd8d568a2edee978ee06a225476f918da20e","tid":550024,"uid":8883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"主攻咪一樣輸反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得救架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"主攻，如果攻到入去心臟地帶，弱隊好多時都係大腳亂清波，唔識做反擊，阿記後衛就可以 collect番個波<br />\n<br />\n阿記成日輸反擊，係因為攻唔到入去心臟地帶，甚至在中場就已經失波，宜家獨扭a山走左，如果再善用支停插，就可以改善問題。"},{"pid":"af2dbc723fc568b34cf73d7e2fd3ff4935d73e9e","tid":550024,"uid":59678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"咁應該點樣踢高速來回球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9780b6b4d18b1f56cc66a2168d5ab91ac6cc0f","tid":550024,"uid":97739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9808ecf81ffbb24bfd92b349be4b80c64416bc0","tid":550024,"uid":143206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886b0c6ae7d3a5a685a7a187eb8039ef8a621487","tid":550024,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re